WEBVTT

00:08.200 --> 00:10.500
My name is 
Melinda Gordon.

00:10.600 --> 00:11.700
I'm married,

00:11.800 --> 00:14.000
I live in a small town,

00:14.100 --> 00:15.900
and I own an antique shop.

00:16.000 --> 00:18.100
I might be just like you

00:18.200 --> 00:19.900
except that from the time
I was a little girl,

00:20.000 --> 00:22.400
I knew that I could
talk to the dead.

00:22.500 --> 00:23.600
It's all right, honey.

00:23.700 --> 00:26.800
Earthbound spirits,
my grandmother called them.

00:26.908 --> 00:29.500
They're stuck here because they have
unfinished business with the living

00:29.603 --> 00:33.307
and they come to me for help.

00:34.706 --> 00:40.005
In order to te you my story,
I have to tell you theirs.

